Kristen and James arrive at the parents' summer house and want nothing but to rest after a long day's drive. What they do not yet know is that this night will turn into the worst night of their lives when three masked strangers show up and disturb the tranquility. These crazy and mysterious stranger finds a sadistic pleasure in terrorizing the young couple. Increasingly developing into a struggle for survival and Kristen and James only chance to survive is by unleashing their most brutal impulses.
